# Description:
#			This master CMakeLists.txt orchestrates the build of FatFs
#			static libraries for all supported cores using ExternalProject.
#			Each core is built as an independent external project with its
#			own CMake configuration and build system.
#
#			Usage:
#				cd Library
#				cmake -B build
#				cmake --build build
#
#			This will build all libraries:
#				- CORTEX_M3/libFatFs.a
#				- CORTEX_M33/libFatFs.a
#				- CORTEX_M4/libFatFs.a
#				- CORTEX_M55/libFatFs.a
#				- CORTEX_M7/libFatFs.a
#				- RV32IMAC/libFatFs.a
#				- RV64IMAFDC/libFatFs.a
